Frequently Asked Questions

Can I cancel my subscription at any time?

Yes, you can cancel your subscription at any time. Your access will continue until the end of your current billing period.

Do you offer refunds?

We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not satisfied with our service, you can request a full refund within 30 days of your purchase.

Can I access courses offline?

Yes, Pro and Enterprise plan subscribers can download courses for offline viewing on mobile devices.

Are the certificates recognized?

Yes, our certificates are recognized by many employers and educational institutions worldwide.

Can I upgrade or downgrade my plan?

Yes, you can upgrade or downgrade your plan at any time. Changes will be reflected in your next billing cycle.

Do you offer team discounts?

Yes, we offer special pricing for teams and organizations. Contact our sales team for more information.
